<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vyntra | Password Reset OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ef4444;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .security-note {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .email-address {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîê Password Reset OTP</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>! üëã</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account with email address <span class="email-address">{{email}}</span>.</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp-label">Your One-Time Password (OTP)</div>
                <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">Enter this code to reset your password</p>
            </div>

            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <p class="warning">‚ö†Ô∏è This OTP will expire in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes for security reasons.</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px;">Please use it immediately to reset your password.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="security-note">
                <p>üîí <strong>Security Notice:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Never share this OTP with anyone</li>
                    <li>Vyntra will never ask for your OTP via phone or email</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this reset, please ignore this email</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>If you continue to have issues, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>¬© {{currentYear}} Vyntra. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
